10 An Act relating to the Office of Juvenile Affairs;
making an appropriation; stating purpose; providing
11 an effective date; and declaring an emergency.
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the Office of
16 Juvenile Affairs from any monies not otherwise appropriated from the
17 General Revenue Fund of the State Treasury for the fiscal year
18 ending June 30, 2027, the sum of Two Hundred Fifty-two Thousand
19 Dollars ($252,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary to
20 carry out the provisions of Enrolled House Bill No. 3755 of the 2nd
21 Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature.
22 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
23 SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
24 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
